===Format===
* '''League Stage''' : ''August 7th - 9th, 2023
** 24 teams.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} qualify for ''Grand Finals''.
<div style="margin-top:12px"/>
* '''Grand Finals''' : ''August 14th - 16th, 2023
** 16 teams.
** 18 matches (6 each day).
